Midgard, Percival</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=araolath>Araolath</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#000000>(4/30/03 11:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=94.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> testing</span><hr size=1> Besides logging in to hit a few greys and fight duels, has anyone gone out and tested how this affects RvR? I don't really care how hard I hit greys or how well I do against Mids in a duel, I'm just concerned about how this will affect Bezerkers role on the battlefield. I realize buffs and end regen make it harder to see the effects of the LA changes, but if you can show logs where you are doing consistently less damage in RvR groups I think that's more useful than a log of hits on grey mobs. Just my two cents. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=94.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=94.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=94.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=94.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/